> **NOTE:** Available in v1.135.0+.

```csharp
class MyStack : Stack

            },

        this.DatabaseGatewayGatewayId1 = ids.Apply(ids => ids.Gateways[0].Id);
        var nameRegex = Output.Create(AliCloud.DatabaseGateway.GetGateways.InvokeAsync(new AliCloud.DatabaseGateway.GetGatewaysArgs
        {
            NameRegex = "^my-Gateway",
        }));
        this.DatabaseGatewayGatewayId2 = nameRegex.Apply(nameRegex => nameRegex.Gateways[0].Id);
    }

    [Output("databaseGatewayGatewayId1")]
    public Output<string> DatabaseGatewayGatewayId1 { get; set; }

    public Output<string> DatabaseGatewayGatewayId2 { get; set; }
}
```

```go
package main

import (
	"github.com/pulumi/pulumi-alicloud/sdk/v3/go/alicloud/databasegateway"

func main() {
	pulumi.Run(func(ctx *pulumi.Context) error {
		ids, err := databasegateway.GetGateways(ctx, &databasegateway.GetGatewaysArgs{
			Ids: []string{
				"example_id",
			},
		}, nil)
		if err != nil {
			return err
		}
		ctx.Export("databaseGatewayGatewayId1", ids.Gateways[0].Id)
		opt0 := "^my-Gateway"
		nameRegex, err := databasegateway.GetGateways(ctx, &databasegateway.GetGatewaysArgs{
			NameRegex: &opt0,
		}, nil)
		if err != nil {
			return err
		}
		ctx.Export("databaseGatewayGatewayId2", nameRegex.Gateways[0].Id)
		return nil
	})
}
```
